title: Tested the previous changes and fixed the bugs.
message: Tested the previous changes and fixed the bugs.

----1----
Changed Carb/Protein/Fat in meals from int to float.
Carb/Protein/Fat in user have remain unchanged.
The total C/P/F for a meal are the base_macro * multiplier but rounded to the nearest int.
Example:
Before adding the Meal: Daily macros consumed where 10c, 20p, 10f
Created a new Meal = Chicken, 0.0c, 33.3p, 4.7f, 100g
Added the same Meal but with different amount = 45g, => multiplier = 45/100 = 0.45
Daily Meal entry = Chicken  0.0c, 33.3*0.45 = 14.985p => rounded to 15p, 4.7f*0.45 = 2.115 => rounded to 2f
After adding the Meal: Daily macros consumed become 10+0 = 0c, 20 + 15 = 35p, 10 +2 = 12f
----2----
Changed serving from int to float.
Made all neccessary GUI changes in order to make app functional (still need to revisit, re-evaluate and optimize them).
